Package com.volvo.softproduct.canparser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CanFrame
    CanFrame class (copy of the one in CPAC SDK) Created to get rid of the dependency to CPAC SDK
    CanParser
    Class used to parse received CAN frame message.
    SignalDefinition
    Class used to describe the signal received in a CAN frame message.
    SignalScale
    Class used to describe a mathematical operation that should be used in the scaling of a parsed signal received in a CAN frame message.
    SignalValue
    Class used to return the parsed signal (value, unit description).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SignalScaleType
    Class used as a ENUM to describe mathematical operations used to scale the received signal from Integers to presentation values.
    SignalType
    Class used as a ENUM to describe if a signal is DOUBLE, LONG or FLAG
